Package: bSims
Type: Package
Title: Bird Point Count Simulator
Version: 0.1-4
Date: 2019-11-22
Author: Peter Solymos [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7337-1740>)
Maintainer: Peter Solymos <solymos@ualberta.ca>
